===Noun===
'''claim'''  (''plural:'' [[claims]])
#A [[demand]] of ownership made for something (eg. claim ownership, claim victory)
#A new statement of truth made about something
#A demand of ownership for previously unowned land (eg. in the gold rush, oil rush)

